data.description: Open foyer & oak hardwood. Oak kitchen w/bar, granite countertops, breakfast area, formal dining room, master BR suite w/cathedral ceiling and walk-in closet, large rooms. New natural gas furnace 2021. New Lenox air unit 2021. New tankless on demand natural gas water heater Nov. 2022. R.O. drinking water system. Updated hardware throughout home. Updated bathroom vanities. 16x26 rear deck, lush landscaping, generous lawn 2+ car garage. New insulation in crawl space. Updates throughout! 14x35 concrete patio and 40x50 concrete turnaround drive. New barn built in 2019 with half the barn with concrete flooring. Natural gas ran to barn & plumbed for bathroom.
